    "path": "src/common/structure",
    "name": "structure",
    "purpose": "Owns shared structural utilities for the common crate. channel.rs defines local and TCP-backed remoc channel helpers whose accept and connect entry points resolve the bind or connect address and the handshake token from config and run a shared-secret token handshake with server-side validation, the ChannelEndpoint client/host/telemetry channel-role selector, and shared net endpoint wrappers. work_queue.rs defines the generic WorkQueue over working and completed maps, including borrowed access through with and clear() cleanup that empties both maps for host-disconnect session reset. mod.rs is namespace and re-export wiring only.",
